msgstr "ຕ້ອງການຄ່າຂີດຈຳກັດສູງສຸດຂອງຊ່ວງ"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "A minimum range limit value is needed"
msgstr "ຕ້ອງການຄ່າຂີດຈຳກັດຕ່ຳສຸດຂອງຊ່ວງ"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"A number indicating which numbering system to use to represent weekdays. By "
"default, counts starting with Sunday = 1."
msgstr ""
"ຕົວເລກທີ່ລະບຸລະບົບການນັບທີ່ໃຊ້ແທນວັນໃນອາທິດ. ໂດຍປົກກະຕິ, ຈະເລີ່ມນັບຈາກວັນອາທິດ = 1."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"A number or string representing which days of the week are considered "
"weekends."
msgstr "ຕົວເລກ ຫຼື ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ລະບຸວ່າວັນໃດໃນອາທິດທີ່ຖືວ່າເປັນວັນຢຸດສຸດສັບປະດາ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "A number raised to a power."
msgstr "ຕົວເລກທີ່ຍົກກຳລັງ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "A number representing the day that a week starts on. Sunday = 1."
msgstr "ຕົວເລກທີ່ລະບຸວັນເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງອາທິດ. ວັນອາທິດ = 1."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "A number representing the way to display ties."
msgstr "ຕົວເລກທີ່ລະບຸຮູບແບບການສະແດງຜົນເມື່ອມີຄ່າເທົ່າກັນ (ties)."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "A number with the sign reversed."
msgstr "ຕົວເລກທີ່ມີເຄື່ອງໝາຍກົງກັນຂ້າມ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "A random number between 0 inclusive and 1 exclusive."
msgstr "ຕົວເລກສຸ່ມລະຫວ່າງ 0 (ລວມ) ຫາ 1 (ບໍ່ລວມ)."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"A range containing the income or payments associated with the investment. "
"The array should contain bot payments and incomes."
msgstr ""
"ຊ່ວງທີ່ປະກອບດ້ວຍລາຍຮັບ ຫຼື ລາຍຈ່າຍທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບການລົງທຶນ. ອາເຣຄວນມີທັງລາຍຈ່າຍ ແລະ ລາຍຮັບ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "A range needs to be defined"
