msgstr "ຄ່າທີ່ value2 ຈະຖືກເພີ່ມຕໍ່ທ້າຍໃສ່."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The value whose rank will be determined."
msgstr "ຄ່າທີ່ຈະຖືກກຳນົດລຳດັບ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The value with which to fill the extra cells in the range."
msgstr "ຄ່າທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ຕື່ມໃສ່ຫ້ອງພິເສດໃນຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The value with which to pad."
msgstr "ຄ່າທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ຕື່ມໃສ່ (pad)."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The value(s) on the x-axis to forecast."
msgstr "ຄ່າໃນແກນ x ທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ຄາດການ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The values of the independent variable(s) corresponding with known_data_y."
msgstr "ຄ່າຂອງຕົວປ່ຽນອິດສະຫຼະທີ່ກົງກັບ known_data_y."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The weekend (%s) must be a string or a number in the range 1-7 or 11-17."
msgstr "ວັນຢຸດສຸດສັບປະດາ (%s) ຕ້ອງເປັນຂໍ້ຄວາມ ຫຼື ຕົວເລກໃນຊ່ວງ 1-7 ຫຼື 11-17."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The weekend must be a number or a string."
msgstr "ວັນຢຸດສຸດສັບປະດາຕ້ອງເປັນຕົວເລກ ຫຼື ຂໍ້ຄວາມ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The weekend must be different from '1111111'."
msgstr "ວັນຢຸດສຸດສັບປະດາຕ້ອງແຕກຕ່າງຈາກ '1111111'."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The window is too small to display multiple side panels."
msgstr "ໜ້າຕ່າງນ້ອຍເກີນໄປທີ່ຈະສະແດງແຜງດ້ານຂ້າງຫຼາຍອັນ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The x coordinate of the endpoint of the line segment for which to calculate "
"the angle from the x-axis."
msgstr "ພິກັດ x ຂອງຈຸດສິ້ນສຸດຂອງເສັ້ນຊື່ທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ຄິດໄລ່ມຸມຈາກແກນ x."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"The y coordinate of the endpoint of the line segment for which to calculate "
"the angle from the x-axis."
msgstr "ພິກັດ y ຂອງຈຸດສິ້ນສຸດຂອງເສັ້ນຊື່ທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ຄິດໄລ່ມຸມຈາກແກນ x."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The year (%s) must be between 0 and 9999 inclusive."
msgstr "ປີ (%s) ຕ້ອງຢູ່ລະຫວ່າງ 0 ຫາ 9999."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The year component of the date."
msgstr "ສ່ວນປະກອບຂອງປີໃນວັນທີ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The yield (%s) must be positive or null."
msgstr "ຜົນຕອບແທນ (%s) ຕ້ອງເປັນຄ່າບວກ ຫຼື ເປັນສູນ (null)."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "The yield of a US Treasury bill based on price."
msgstr "ຜົນຕອບແທນຂອງພັນທະບັດຄັງເງິນສະຫະລັດໂດຍອີງຕາມລາຄາ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/list/list_functions.js:0
msgid "There is no list with id \"%s\""
msgstr "ບໍ່ມີລາຍການທີ່ມີ id \"%s\""

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "There is no match for the selected separator in the selection"
msgstr "ບໍ່ມີສິ່ງທີ່ກົງກັບຕົວແຍກທີ່ເລືອກໃນສ່ວນທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "There is no pivot with id \"%s\""
msgstr "ບໍ່ມີ pivot ທີ່ມີ id \"%s\""

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"There must be both positive and negative values in [payment_amount, "
"present_value, future_value]."
msgstr ""
"ຕ້ອງມີທັງຄ່າບວກ ແລະ ຄ່າລົບໃນ [payment_amount, present_value, future_value]."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "There must be both positive and negative values in cashflow_amounts."
msgstr "ຕ້ອງມີທັງຄ່າບວກ ແລະ ຄ່າລົບໃນ cashflow_amounts."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "Third quartile (75th percentile)"
msgstr "ຄວໍໄທລ໌ທີສາມ (ເປີເຊັນໄທລ໌ທີ 75)"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"This dimension contains a lot of values (%s), and might slow down the pivot "
"table."
msgstr "ມິຕິນີ້ບັນຈຸຄ່າເປັນຈຳນວນຫຼາຍ (%s), ແລະ ອາດເຮັດໃຫ້ຕາຕະລາງ pivot ຊ້າລົງ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"This formula has over 1000 parts. It can't be processed properly, consider "
"splitting it into multiple cells"
msgstr ""
"ສູດນີ້ມີຫຼາຍກວ່າ 1000 ສ່ວນ. ມັນບໍ່ສາມາດປະມວນຜົນໄດ້ຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງ, ກະລຸນາພິຈາລະນາແຍກມັນອອກເປັນຫຼາຍຫ້ອງ"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/currency/formulas.js:0
msgid ""
"This function takes in two currency codes as arguments, and returns the "
"exchange rate from the first currency to the second as float."
msgstr ""
"ຟັງຊັນນີ້ຮັບລະຫັດສະກຸນເງິນສອງອັນເປັນອາຄິວເມນ, ແລະ ສົ່ງຄືນອັດຕາແລກປ່ຽນຈາກສະກຸນເງິນທຳອິດໄປຫາສະກຸນເງິ"
"ນທີສອງເປັນເລກທົດສະນິຍົມ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "This operation is not allowed due to an overlapping frozen pane."
msgstr ""
"ການດຳເນີນການນີ້ບໍ່ຖືກອະນຸຍາດເນື່ອງຈາກມີການຊ້ອນທັບກັບແຖບທີ່ຢຸດສະງັກໄວ້ (frozen pane)."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "This operation is not allowed with multiple selections."
msgstr "ການດຳເນີນການນີ້ບໍ່ຖືກອະນຸຍາດເມື່ອມີການເລືອກຫຼາຍລາຍການ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"This operation is not possible due to a merge. Please remove the merges "
"first than try again."
msgstr ""
"ການດຳເນີນການນີ້ບໍ່ສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ເນື່ອງຈາກມີການຮວມຫ້ອງ. ກະລຸນາຍົກເລີກການຮວມຫ້ອງກ່ອນ ແລ້ວລອງໃໝ່ອີກຄັ້"
"ງ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.xml:0
msgid "This pivot has no cell missing on this sheet"
msgstr "pivot ນີ້ບໍ່ມີຫ້ອງທີ່ຫາຍໄປໃນຊີດນີ້"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.xml:0
msgid "This pivot is not used"
msgstr "pivot ນີ້ບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກໃຊ້"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.xml:0
msgid "This range is invalid"
msgstr "ຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນນີ້ບໍ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.xml:0
msgid ""
"This tool analyzes formulas for patterns and highlights inconsistencies. Irregularities\n"
"            may indicate potential errors in formula structures, references or arguments."
msgstr ""
"ເຄື່ອງມືນີ້ວິເຄາະສູດເພື່ອຊອກຫາຮູບແບບ ແລະ ເນັ້ນຈຸດທີ່ບໍ່ສອດຄ່ອງກັນ. ຄວາມຜິດປົກກະຕິ\n"
"            ອາດບົ່ງບອກເຖິງຂໍ້ຜິດພາດທີ່ອາດເກີດຂຶ້ນໃນໂຄງສ້າງສູດ, ການອ້າງອີງ ຫຼື ອາຄິວເມນ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.xml:0
msgid ""
"This tool analyzes spreadsheet formulas for patterns and highlights "
"inconsistencies. Irregularities may indicate potential errors in formula "
"structures, references, or arguments. (Click to turn off)"
msgstr ""
"ເຄື່ອງມືນີ້ວິເຄາະສູດໃນສະເປຣດຊີດເພື່ອຊອກຫາຮູບແບບ ແລະ ເນັ້ນຈຸດທີ່ບໍ່ສອດຄ່ອງກັນ. ຄວາມຜິດປົກກະຕິອາດບົ່ງບອກ"
"ເຖິງຂໍ້ຜິດພາດທີ່ອາດເກີດຂຶ້ນໃນໂຄງສ້າງສູດ, ການອ້າງອີງ, ຫຼື ອາຄິວເມນ. (ຄລິກເພື່ອປິດ)"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "This will overwrite data in the subsequent columns. Split anyway?"
msgstr "ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະຂຽນທັບຂໍ້ມູນໃນຖັນຖັດໆໄປ. ຕ້ອງການແຍກຫຼືບໍ່?"

