msgstr "ບໍ່ວ່າຄ່ານັ້ນບໍ່ແມ່ນຂໍ້ຄວາມຫຼືບໍ່."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
