"Whether or not to divide text around each character contained in delimiter."
msgstr "ຈະແບ່ງຂໍ້ຄວາມຕາມແຕ່ລະຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ຢູ່ໃນຕົວແຍກຫຼືບໍ່."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"Whether or not to remove empty text messages from the split results. The "
"default behavior is to treat         consecutive delimiters as one (if "
"TRUE). If FALSE, empty cells values are added between consecutive "
"delimiters."
msgstr ""
"ຈະເອົາຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ວ່າງອອກຈາກຜົນລັບການແຍກຫຼືບໍ່. ພຶດຕິກຳເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນການຖືວ່າຕົວແຍກທີ່ຕິດກັນເປັນອັນດຽວ (ຫາກເ"
"ປັນ TRUE). ຫາກເປັນ FALSE, ຈະມີການເພີ່ມຄ່າຫ້ອງວ່າງລະຫວ່າງຕົວແຍກທີ່ຕິດກັນ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "Whether the match is case-sensitive."
msgstr "ການຈັບຄູ່ຕ້ອງກົງກັນຕາມຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່-ນ້ອຍຫຼືບໍ່."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "Whether the provided value is even."
msgstr "ບໍ່ວ່າຄ່າທີ່ລະບຸນັ້ນເປັນເລກຄູ່ຫຼືບໍ່."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "Whether the referenced cell is empty"
msgstr "ບໍ່ວ່າຫ້ອງທີ່ອ້າງອີງນັ້ນວ່າງຫຼືບໍ່"

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"Whether to consider the values in data in descending or ascending order."
msgstr "ຈະພິຈາລະນາຄ່າໃນຂໍ້ມູນແບບຈັດລຽງຈາກໃຫຍ່ຫາໜ້ອຍ ຫຼື ໜ້ອຍຫາໃຫຍ່."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "Whether to filter the data by columns or by rows."
msgstr "ຈະກັ່ນຕອງຂໍ້ມູນຕາມຖັນ ຫຼື ຕາມແຖວ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"Whether to ignore certain types of values. By default, no values are "
"ignored."
msgstr "ຈະລະເລີຍຄ່າບາງປະເພດຫຼືບໍ່. ໂດຍເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ, ຈະບໍ່ມີການລະເລີຍຄ່າໃດໆ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "Whether to ignore empty cells."
msgstr "ຈະລະເລີຍຫ້ອງທີ່ວ່າງຫຼືບໍ່."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "Whether to include the column titles or not."
msgstr "ຈະລວມເອົາຫົວຂໍ້ຖັນຫຼືບໍ່."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "Whether to include the measure titles row or not."
msgstr "ຈະລວມເອົາແຖວຫົວຂໍ້ການວັດແທກຫຼືບໍ່."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "Whether to include total/sub-totals or not."
msgstr "ຈະລວມເອົາຜົນລວມທັງໝົດ/ຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍຫຼືບໍ່."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
