msgstr "ຈະສົ່ງຄືນສະເພາະລາຍການທີ່ບໍ່ມີຄ່າຊ້ຳກັນຫຼືບໍ່."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid ""
"Whether to switch to straight-line depreciation when the depreciation is "
"greater than the declining balance calculation."
msgstr ""
"ຈະປ່ຽນໄປໃຊ້ການຄິດໄລ່ຄ່າເສື່ອມລາຄາແບບເສັ້ນຊື່ຫຼືບໍ່ ເມື່ອຄ່າເສື່ອມລາຄານັ້ນຫຼາຍກວ່າການຄິດໄລ່ແບບຍອດຫຼຸດລົງ."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
msgid "Whether to treat the end of text as a delimiter."
msgstr "ຈະຖືວ່າສ່ວນທ້າຍຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມເປັນຕົວແຍກຫຼືບໍ່."

#. module: spreadsheet
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet/static/src/o_spreadsheet/o_spreadsheet.js:0
